    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .ConsPlusNonformat {font-family: 'Courier New'; font-size: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 299.23545706371px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">га</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 299.23545706371px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берувчининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 299.23545706371px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">томонидан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(Суднинг ҳал қилув қарори ижросини кечиктириш тўғрисида)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бераман ушбу аризани шу ҳақдаким, <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Ҳал қилув қарори қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> кунда </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Ҳал қилув қарорини қабул қилган суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> суди томонидан даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Иш бўйича даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг менга нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Даъвогарнинг даъво аризаси мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ҳақидаги фуқаролик иши кўриб чиқилиб, даъвогарнинг даъво талаби қаноатлантирилган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ҳозирда менга мазкур иш юзасидан чиқарилган ҳал қилув қарори ижросини таъминлаш мақсадида </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Ҳал қилув қарори ижросини таъминлаётган МИБ бўлими номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> бўлимидан даъвогарнинг фойдасига </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ҳал қилув қарорида даъвогарнинг фойдасига нима ундириш белгиланган</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ундириш, давлат божи учун </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Ундирилиши белгиланган давлат божи миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм тўлаш лозимлиги ҳақида огоҳлантириш хати келган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бугунги кунда ушбу пулларни тўлашга имкониятим йўқ, чунки оилавий аҳволим оғир, ўзим ҳеч қаерда ишламайман, кам таъминланган оилалар ҳисобида тураман, шу сабабли Ўзбекистон Республикаси ФПКнинг 454-моддасига асосан ҳал қилув қарори ижросини кечиктиришингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Илова: </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Аризага асос сифатида илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар рўйхати</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ф.</span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}И.О.си </span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">_____________________</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 212.14404432133px;\">\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 212.14404432133px;\">\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
